	<h1 class="title">除了《辐射 4》拿大奖，今年游戏奥斯卡还有一些其他事儿</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/57300/small/57300.jpg?1427187252" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐舒畅 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-02-21 08:00:20 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/22606/medium/22606.jpg?1455944417" alt="" />			
	</div>
